_json.description: Free Printable Planner - A vertical layout with everything you need in it to organize and plan your month. 24 pages. Monthly calendar on 2 pages, Reflection on last month, To do page, week on 2 pages, notes pages, and dotted pages. Beautiful images of flowers reminding us of some English gardens. Dimensions are Letter US, but you can resize it easily for the Classic Happy Planner. Explications to do it in the post. | The Printable Collection
